# data-models

## Core Trading Data Models

### Bot Configuration Model
- Trading pair configuration (regex: /^[A-Z0-9]{2,20}USDT$/)
- Risk parameters:
  - Dynamic leverage (2x-7x)
  - Adaptive stop-loss (1.5%-4.0%)
  - Volume-based position sizing
- Performance tracking metrics
- Real-time state management

### Performance Metrics Model 
- Win/Loss ratio tracking
- Drawdown calculations 
- Fee estimation
- 30-day performance (40% weight)
- 24h momentum (20% weight)
- Volume scoring (20% weight)
- Volatility metrics (20% weight)

### Trading Profile Model
- Experience level classification (4 tiers)
- Risk tolerance categories:
  - Conservative
  - Moderate 
  - Aggressive
- Trading capital brackets
- Exchange preferences (Bybit/OKX)

### Paper Trading Model
- Virtual account balance tracking
- Trade execution logging
- Real-time balance updates
- Bot attribution tracking
- Performance simulation data

### Bot Activity Model
- Real-time state inference
- Health monitoring metrics
- Execution state classification
- Time-based activity analysis
- Trade limit controls

### Strategy Optimization Model
- AI-based parameter recommendations
- Confidence scoring metrics
- Historical optimization logs
- Performance validation data
- Strategy version control

## Integration Models

